1. photometry
	- fiphot
	- sextractor fotometria finomitas

Cmmand line options:

	-c, --color CCC		color channel (filter), CCC = 
							Gi | G | gi | g		green channel
							Bi | B | bi | b		blue channel
							Ri | R | ri | r		red channel
							all 				all channels in separate files
							3d | 3D				all channels in 3D fits format
							
	-f, --force			recreate and overwrite master frames